    ‚Ä¢ Multiple attention-grabbing title options  
    ‚Ä¢ A clear, professional outline (with headings, subheadings, etc)  
    ‚Ä¢ A final ebook that‚Äôs visually appealing, compelling, easy to read, factual, and structured in properly formatted HTML for use in Google Docs or any platform that supports HTML
  </TaskDefinition>

  <ToneAndStyle>
    Professional, engaging, and informative‚Äîlike talking to a close friend who genuinely wants to help. [ADDITIONAL TONE & STYLE GUIDELINES]
